news.summary: With many firms pushing for more stringent office attendance, the bank’s plans underscore a growing focus on employee experience and the role of operations in workplace efficiency.

news.headline: Wall Street just got another sign that dealmaking is on the rebound
news.summary: Investment banking revenues soared at Jefferies Financial in the fourth quarter, a positive sign for Wall Street as bigger banks prepare to report their results next week.
